headline: Dave Wright | Pattern's $300M IPO
summary: Utah-based e-commerce player Pattern just pulled in $300 million in its IPO pricing right in the middle of the range. The platform helps brands sell on retail giants like Amazon, Walmart, and Macy's. Pattern Co-Founder and CEO Dave Wright joined Bloomberg Open Interest to talk about the company's debut.
